Today we are excited to talk about and put to the test @emangrizzle1's 'Dining With The Dead' Pro Model Deck! EMAN himself worked closely with the R&D department to design this particular shape, so we are super stoked to test this one out for ourselves! Keeping the legend train rolling, the Artwork on this one is done by none other than Mr. @jimbophillips. If you do not grab this one to shred, grab one for the wall while you can! We put Santa Cruz Skateboards Brand Manager Andrew Cannon to the test with three NEW challenges to find out how this setup skates! Hit our @youtube channel to watch now, then let us know in the comments below what challenges we should throw in the bins next!

Ricta Wheel Dynamics Chrome Cores 99a 53mm

Class is in session! Today we are stoked to link up with @maurcoy to learn the secrets of the Ollie from the Prince of Pop himself. From foot placement, to rolling vs stationary, Maurio breaks down everything about how he learned ollies, what runs through his head while he is getting ready to pop an ollie, and how the ollie applies to many other tricks in skateboarding. If you are just getting in to skating, this is a great first trick to learn. Let us know in the comments which tricks we should cover next, and swipe 🆙 in our story to join Maurio for our @youtube premiere!
🎥: @_nickhanson
🎬: @tylerlodzinski
#SantaCruzSkateboards

node.text:
Today we are thrilled to sit down with multi talented musician, father, and skateboarder Anthony Green aka @anthonygreen666 at his music studio in Doylestown, PA. You may have heard of Anthony through his work with bands like @circasurvive, @saosinofficial, #fuckinwhatever or just his solo Anthony Green moniker. What you might not have known is that Anthony shares a deep passion for skateboarding and music and is thankful for the lessons his kids learn through those shared arts. Anthony also discusses writing new music during the pandemic, why he works on so many different projects and how stoked he is to get back on the road. For any skateboarder, musician or parent this is a must see. We can’t wait to see you on the road, Anthony! Hit our @youtube channel to watch now!
🎥: @thekillatapes @trevarcushing
🎬: @richievaldez
#SantaCruzSkateboards
